{"tid":2019593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"飛虎隊, 機場特警隊, 新界南機動部隊參與「虎嘯」反恐演習","createTime":"2020-05-16T11:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T05:23:04.000Z","uid":53705,"like":15,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"70182fd1ef667198d7bdc35c4a201c5214c8ab02","tid":2019593,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"警方在機場進行代號為「虎嘯」的反恐演習，應對劫機事故。<br />\n<br />\n反恐演習於前日清晨進行，旨在測試警方的反恐應變計畫及程序。參與單位包括機場特警組、飛虎隊及新界南總區警察機動部隊。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，機場特警組人員藉此機會演練在機艙內搜捕企圖劫機者，並聯同飛虎隊及機動部隊人員進行處理受影響人士的程序。演習亦加入「即時戰術介入」的訓練元素，有助各人員進一步提升處理相關恐襲事故的能力。<br />\n<br />\n香港整體恐襲威脅級別仍然維持「中度」。警方表明會不斷加強反恐能力和準備，以應對任何突如其來的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/482736c3-3cfb-4beb-b123-60e94d98a309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F482736c3-3cfb-4beb-b123-60e94d98a309&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=2336ee94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/482736c3-3cfb-4beb-b123-60e94d98a309</a><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇??"},{"pid":"aef4989e55e56d805cbbb21328a972eb57d25d37","tid":2019593,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1760638/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4-%E8%99%8E%E5%98%AF-%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92-%E6%90%9C%E6%8D%95%E5%8A%AB%E6%A9%9F%E7%8A%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1760638%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E8%2599%258E%25E5%2598%25AF-%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%25BF%2592-%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%258D%2595%25E5%258A%25AB%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%258A%25AF&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=2bb90392\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1760638%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%